    <p>Motivation</p>
    <p>Existing energy measurement methods are not suited for energy-based billing or accurate energy profiling of applications.</p>
    <p>ExternalMeasurement</p>
    <p>, Accurate energy/power values / Limited to machine-level granularity / Expensive deployment for data centers</p>
    <p>Inference-BasedEstimation</p>
    <p>, Adjustable granularity and resolution / Calibration required for every system / 8% to 10% inaccuracy</p>
